Here are the categories you can use to group the fields for your voting registration form:

Personal Information:

Full Name
ID Number
Date of Birth
Address
Contact Details

Verification and Eligibility:

Proof of Address
Citizenship
Voting District

Additional Information:

Preferred Language
Disability Status
Political Party Affiliation (optional)

Optional Information:
Gender
Marital Status

Consent:
Consent Statement for Data Collection and Processing

